Lawyers should follow the highest standards of professional ethics and inspire trust and confidence in society.
Mr. Ditta betrayed that trust and tried to cover up his profession.
Mr. Ditt ' s investigation was conducted by Lancashire ' s Specially Dangerous Organized Crime Unit, which had already reached his verdict in three cases of cocaine possession, and now also on obstruction of justice, demonstrating our desire to achieve just punishment for criminals.
