Esser proposes to equate the insult of patriotic feelings to extremism
For the legislative protection of patriotic feelings of citizens from provocations and insults directed against Russia, "Fair Russia" proposes to equate the insult of patriotic feelings to extremist activities and punish it with five years in prison.
