Simultaneously with the recalculation of labour pensions in November this year, the minimum and social pensions, allowances, increases and supplementary pensions will be recalculated in connection with the increase in the budget of the subsistence minimum on average per capita.
BPM for the period from November 1, 2013 to January 31, 2014 was approved by the government in the amount of Br1 million 47 thousand 530 - by 2.1% higher than in the period from August 1 to October 31.
